name: RandomElementFromList
description:
Automation script that can be used as a transformer, to return a random selection of elements from a list of items.

Type: Automation Script
Inputs:
            1. value - list of items to pick from. Data type - array
            2. count - number of random items to return. Data type - int
Output:
            1. List of items, randomly selected from the input list. Data type - array. Length = count
author: Aneesha More
